VFS::GnomeVFS is a driver ( and standalone ) module for VFS.  It binds in the
functionality supplied by the gnome-vfs library of the Gnome project for accessing
files across various environments file://, http://, https://, ssh:// etc.



perl Makefile.PL
make 
make test
make install

Dance.

for more details:

perldoc VFS::GnomeVFS

http://developer.gnome.org/doc/API/gnome-vfs/index.html

